headline: Broadridge Acquires Signal, Accelerating Global Digital Communications Expansion
summary: Global Fintech leader Broadridge Financial Solutions, Inc. (NYSE: BR), today announced that it has acquired Signal, a leader in transforming customer communications for financial services and social sector firms in the UK.
